Hello All,
I am not exactly a new member, but it's been about 8 years since=
 I was a part of your community. I return in need of as much historical ass=
istance y'all can provide.
I am a writer and back then I had written a stor=
y that took place in 1866, the end of the Meiji restoration. But now I find=
 myself returning to this story and re-writing it with a beginning in 1863-=
64. It is on its way to being my creative writing thesis and as such I want=
 to capture more of this amazing and very interesting time.=A0
I want more =
of a focus on those who were involved, mostly from Satsuma and Choshu. Kido=
 Koin and Kawakami Gensai being two of the supporting characters.


I look =
forward to reading your post and posting my own entries and such


See ya a=
round
Sarah
